{"tid":453884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱克伯格北京會習近平　以中文大讚中國發展令人震撼","createTime":"2017-10-31T15:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T05:25:32.000Z","uid":88681,"like":5,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7bdc939de2d3a459b0b6d041b81b70438bda34","tid":453884,"uid":88681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/TIM_rhtd4_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FTIM_rhtd4_1200x0.png&h=d76cad43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nFacebook近年積極爭取打入中國市場，創辦人朱克伯格（Mark Zuckerberg）聯同蘋果行政總裁庫克等科技巨頭，昨日於北京與國家主席習近平會面。據官媒《人民日報》報道，朱克伯格以中文作開場白，又借用習近平十九大報告中「不忘初心」一詞，大讚中國發展。<br />\n<br />\n昨日（30日）習近平在北京人民大會堂，會見清華大學經濟管理學院顧問委員會，出席會議的除了有朱克伯格外，亦有蘋果行政總裁庫克、黑石集團董事長蘇世民等。<br />\n<br />\n據《人民日報》報道，朱克伯格一開始以中文發言，大讚「中國的發展令人震撼」。他借用十九大報告中的「不忘初心」一詞，稱中國在過去30多年間，已使七億多人脫貧，在此方面的成就超過其他國家，希望中國未來30年能繼續取得如此進步。<br />\n<br />\n他又指應加強不同文明相互理解，「希望世界各地的人更加了解中國&hellip;&hellip;如果世界上幾十億人都能夠聽到中國的聲音，世界會變得更美好。」<br />\n<br />\n報道亦指，庫克對習近平在全球治理方面展現的領導力深表讚歎，稱自己與中國的友誼已經有30年。他認為創新和技術來自於開放與合作，「我們希望與中國共建繁榮的未來」。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook發言人證實朱克伯格身處北京，但拒絕透露訪京的詳細行程。蘋果發言人則拒絕就庫克的行程及會面，作出任何評論。<br />\n<br />\n朱克伯格近年在中國頗為活躍，今年9月Facebook委任曾在內地政府部門任職的William Shuai，專門負責處理與中國政府的關係事務。外界普遍認為，FB此舉是為了就打入中國龐大市場而開路。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/technology/%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2585%258B%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2592%25BC%2F&d=183tMSu8fj4vslgrYfXG%2BQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5dd2ab8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Ftechnology%2F%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2585%258B%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%259C%2583%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%2596%2587%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25AE%259A%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%259C%2587%25E6%2592%25BC%2F&h=990c9cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/technology/%E6%9C%B1%E5%85%8B%E4%BC%AF%E6%A0%BC%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E4%BB%A5%E4%B8%AD%E6%96%87%E5%A4%A7%E8%AE%9A%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E9%9C%87%E6%92%BC/</a><br />\n<br />\n奶共奶到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f57bbd8f04a680d867732c75153bca81b7afcd","tid":453884,"uid":22858,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:13:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>條友真係巨型Sucker，勁過曬堆五毛</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https:/